dialogStrings:
[Save Point]
Access the Menu and select
{PURPLE}[SAVE]{WHITE} to save your game.

Reno
“You're finally here.
Let's split up.”{PAUSE}“You do whatever it takes,
but don't endanger Elena.”{PAUSE}“Don't worry.
We won't do anything to her,
{Yuffie}.”{PAUSE}“For now…”

Reno
“Stop fooling around.
The enemy's not gonna
wait for us, you know!”

Reno
“You all thought they might be here
too, huh? We were way off.”{PAUSE}“There's no way they could get this far.”

{Cloud}
“Can't go through here…
That flame would
fry us in an instant.”
“"The Scale of the Sea God" shines!”

Corneo
“Hmm!
Delicious…scrumptious!
I think I've just found a new HOBBY!”

Elena
“He…hey, I'm a 'Turk'!
You can't get away with this!!”

{Yuffie}
“Oh GAWD!
If I knew this was gonna happen,
I would've taken those rope
lessons more seriously!!”

Corneo
“Hmm!!!
I've made my choice!
My companion for the night will be…”

{Yuffie}
“GROSS-NESS!”{PAUSE}“Don't mess with me old man!
You don't even have any Materia!”

Corneo
“Oooooh!
And she's saucy, too!
Wheee! Wheee!”

“Hey, hey, hey!
That's as far as you go!”

Corneo
“Hee-haw.
What…what's goin' on!? Who's there?”

{Tifa}
“That fall into the trap really hurt!”

{Aeris}
“You just don't get it, do you?”

{Cid}
“Maybe God'd forgive an ugly ^#@# like you,
but I won't!”

{Red XIII}
“Hurry and let the two go!”

{Vincent}
“I don't care what you're doing,
so much as the idiotic way you're doing it…”

{Cait Sith}
“Listen you stupid, slimy, sleazy old scab bag!
If you want to get women,
there's such a thing as the RIGHT way!”

Corneo
“Be quiet!
None of you know how much
I've suffered since then…”

{Tifa}
“We don't want to hear it!
Just let them go!”

{Cid}
“I don't really give a damn!
You're gonna let them go,
or else I'm gonna break your arm!”

{Cloud}
“I don't really care!
Let {Yuffie} and Elena go!”

Corneo
“Hmm…You guys are serious.
…Good, good.”{PAUSE}“…this time I'm not
fooling around either…”

Corneo
“Why did you kill my little Aps?”{PAUSE}“I'm gonna make you PLAY with my new pet,
so you won't interfere
in my search for a bride!”

{Cid}
“Don't be such a poor loser, old man!”

Corneo
“Just listen to me - it won't take long.”{PAUSE}“Why do you think a bad guy like me would
swallow his pride and plead for his life?”{PAUSE} 1 Because he's ready to die
2 Because he's sure to win
3 Because he's clueless

Corneo
“Once I push this button, they'll fall
and we'll have SQUASHED TOMATOES!”

{Cid}
“So this is how a loser lives?”

Corneo
“Now, give me your women too!”

Corneo
“Ha, ha, ha, ha!
I guess I have the last laugh!”

Reno
“You knew this was gonna happen ever since
you leaked that secret.”{PAUSE}“We're going to take care of you…
personally.”

Corneo
“DAMMIT! Then they're
all comin' with me!”

Reno
“All right, Corneo.
This'll be over quick, so listen up.”{PAUSE}“Why do you think we went to all the trouble of
teaming up with those guys to get you?”{PAUSE} 1 Because we're ready to die
2 Because we're sure to win
3 Because we're clueless

Elena
“Oh, thank you very much!”{PAUSE}“I never thought you'd come…”

Reno
“Elena,
don't act so weak.”{PAUSE}“You're a Turk!”

{Cait Sith}
“So you do have some good in you.”

{Vincent}
“It would appear thanks are in order…”

Reno
“Yes…this is Reno.”{PAUSE}“Yes…Yes…
I'll get on it right away.”

Reno
“Yeah,
they want us to find {Cloud}…”
“Only those from Wutai may enter the tower!”{PAUSE}“I'll have to ask for you to leave!”

“Hey! I can't stand liars!
Leave this tower at once!”

“Oh, Miss {Yuffie}!
Will you climb the pagoda today?”
Yeah
No way!

“Then I, Gorky,
will be your opponent on the first floor!”

“Miss {Yuffie}!
You cannot go on to the second floor
unless you defeat me!”

“Yo! They call me Shake!
I'll be watchin' your fight with Gorky!”

Shake
“Hmm, I thought you were just a girl,
but you handled that pretty good!”{PAUSE}“Let's see how you do on next one…”

Gorky
“In my opinion, you need more training!
I am disappointed!”

Shake
“No good!
You must beat Gorky!
Are you mocking this Pagoda?”

Shake
“Are you blind?
I'm right here!”

Shake
“Heh! Punk.
At least I'm not some baby bimbo!”

Shake
“See what I mean?
That anger's what makes you
so immature!”{PAUSE}“Don't pat yourself on the back
until you beat me!”

Shake
“'bout the only thing you do really good is breathe!
Are you sure you wanna fight?”
Stop yappin'!
I'll forgive you

Shake
“Here I go, brat!
Speed Change!”

Shake
“You don't belong here!
This is the Wutai Temple of Martial Arts!”

Shake
“Hey, you there!
Don't ignore me!”

Shake
“So you're just talk after all.
Brat!”

Chekhov
“You can't go to the next floor
unless you beat Shake.”

Chekhov
“Ho, ho, ho…
It's been a while since I felt pain…

“So even Shake's been defeated.
It's been a while since you
had to fight, eh Chekhov?”

Chekhov
“Unfortunately, this is as far as it goes.
Staniv, you watch over there.”

{Yuffie}
“That ain't going to happen!
I'll teach you about the strength of youth!”

Chekhov
“Keep mouthing off like that, little girl,
and you're going to get burned.”
I got insurance.
Let's get this over, ya' old geez.

Chekhov
“Ho, ho, ho.
We'll see if you still talk like that
after you taste some of my Sacred Magic…”

Chekhov
“Ho, ho, ho.
What did you expect from a child
barely out of diapers!?”

Chekhov
“I can't believe you beat me…”

Staniv
“This should be interesting!
It's been a long time since I've
used my powers to their fullest…”

Chekhov
“Ho, ho, ho!
What does a immature child know…?”

Staniv
“This is the average person's limit?”

Chekhov
“That being the case, we have
nothing further to discuss.”

Chekhov
“How dare they think
they could sneak past us?”

Staniv
“First, Chekhov will keep you company…”

{Yuffie}
“Huh? Who am I supposed to beat?”

Staniv
“The rule is the best fighter on
each floor will be your opponent…
This is a five-storied pagoda,
but the fourth floor is the highest{PAUSE}you'll ever get--no one has ever
defeated me--Master of Weaponry!”{PAUSE}“You still want to try?”
Just come on!!
I'll pass!

Staniv
“How unfortunate!
It was over before I could even
put all my strength into it…”

Shake
“Oh, ho!
Maybe you're not as
big a child as we thought!”

Chekhov
“Of course.
If WE lost to her…”

Staniv
“You have defeated four of our
best, but now you will have to
face HIM!”

Staniv
“If it were not for Miss {Yuffie},
I wouldn't be facing him…”

Staniv
“You didn't seem like someone who could
get to the fourth floor so easily.”

Godo
“I'm glad you made it this far,
{Yuffie}!”

Godo
“I'll answer that by having you
try your skills against me!”{PAUSE}“Hold nothing back.
Come as if you're trying to kill me!
If you don't…then I'll have to kill you!”

Godo
“Ohhh! And what was that!?
Come back when you get more training!”

{Yuffie}
“I'll show you this time, you old Fart-meister!”

Godo
“Come at me with all you have!
OMNI-Change!!”

Godo
“It's time I gave this
to you, {Yuffie}…”{PAUSE}“This is Leviathan Materia.
Take it.”

Godo
“…I thought I'd give it to you,
but you have no room for it.”{PAUSE}“Then, come back for it later.
And don't forget!”

Godo
“Leviathan Materia?
Oh! So you DID remember.”
“Well it's yours, go ahead and take it!”

Staniv
“But, Lord Godo.
Leviathan Materia should only be given
to the person who conquers and takes
over this Pagoda.
That is our custom…”

{Yuffie}
“CUSTOM, CUSTOM, CUSTOM…
I'm so sick of hearing that!”{PAUSE}“It's so stupid!”

{Yuffie}
“What 'bout all of you?
With all your power…”{PAUSE}“Are you satisfied being cooped up
in this tower?”

{Yuffie}
“You too, dad!
Just because you lost the war, did”{PAUSE}“you have to turn Wutai into a place like this?”

{Yuffie}
“You turned Wutai into a cheesy resort town
peddling to tourists…”

{Yuffie}
“How dare you!?
Da-chao Statue and Leviathan are ashamed!!”

Godo
“Forgive me…
It's all my fault…”

Gorky
“What are you saying,
Lord Godo?”

Godo
“Losing the war…turning Wutai into this.
It was all my fault…”

Godo
“{Yuffie}…”{PAUSE}“I am the same now as I was
before when I wanted war.”{PAUSE}“But, after losing,
I began to think…”{PAUSE}“Is strength for beating enemies”{PAUSE}“…or just something to show-off?”{PAUSE}“Might begets might.”{PAUSE}“The same as Shinra.”

Godo
“I knew you were looking for Materia
for the good of Wutai.”{PAUSE}“But, the reason I hide my strength now,
is also for the good of Wutai…”{PAUSE}“And now, I realize both are necessary…”{PAUSE}“Strength without determination means
nothing.
And determination without strength
is equally useless…”

Godo
“You there, please take {Yuffie}
with you!”{PAUSE}“I perceive that you all have both
determination and strength!”

{Cid}
“Well, just imagine you're on a
big airship, and leave
the rest to ol' {Cid}!”

{Cait Sith}
“If you put it that way,
we can't refuse…”

{Red XIII}
“As long as she doesn't interfere!”

{Aeris}
“All right.
We'll take her with us.”

{Vincent}
“Hmm…
You may come if you want to…”

{Barret}
“Jus' don't do nothin'
funny to our Materia!”

Godo
“I'll take care of the Five Sacred Gods
until you return!”{PAUSE}“Go!
And come back alive!”

Godo
“After their battle is over…{PAUSE}Do you think they'll still want
all their Materia?”

Godo
“Go!
Fight till the end!
But return…”{PAUSE}“With the Materia!”

Staniv
“Miss {Yuffie}.
Your feelings for Wutai are the same
as Lord Godo's.
Always remember that…”

Chekhov
“She's always like this.
It'll be rough on you.”

Shake
“You say there's some unusual Materia where
the underground pipe is!?”{PAUSE}“But, first you gotta get if from a monster
and unless you use your head,
you won't be able to do it.”

Gorky
“Miss {Yuffie}.
We pray for your success!”

Gorky
“Oh, you there!
How is Miss {Yuffie} doing?”

Gorky
“Winning Miss {Yuffie}'s heart
must mean you have tremendous skill.”

Shake
“Compared to me,
all of you are nothin' but a buncha babies.”

Chekhov
“Managing that girl must be
exceedingly difficult.”

Staniv
“I would like to fight you,
however the Five Sacred Gods can
only compete with those from Wutai…”

Godo
“Go!
Fight till the end!
But return…”{PAUSE}“With the Mat-”{PAUSE}“Take care of the Materia!!”

Godo
“Please look after your Mat-”{PAUSE}“I mean, look after {Yuffie}!”

You can not take on any more Materia.
Please discard some Materia.
